ank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1</a><br />\n有消息嘗試用舉牌方式同人講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1</a><br />\n我覺得今日散水無錯，互屌先係真中計<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1</a><br />\n[賽後檢討] 今日機場有無散水既都麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1</a><br />\n下次搞再機場唔該幫下啲旅客<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1</a><br />\n今日機場事件有少少諗法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1</a><br />\n我係散水撚，我係嚟道歉嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好需要你幫手報料/update/宣傳呀"},{"pid":"641bd0e4c3087e3a247af3eb79084d1b6926bc42","tid":1458592,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fce4e8b80afbe69d6df538f9391f00baf489e50","tid":1458592,"uid":215270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"機場m記加大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:40:51.000Z","msg":"話時話機場間M記係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a246ffc5c3c07a80fcee36c6a077677a54716b23","tid":1458592,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7db54495d9fbbee1be14e1e41218e7034e88112f","tid":1458592,"uid":285118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"有無人要同我一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1點食到1點"},{"pid":"bcacf56126ae7079d9e88ef4846439d7a063a234","tid":1458592,"uid":17